HR Opis mjesta Brodarica

Malo, mirno mjesto pogodno za obitelji, 3&#39;000 stanovnika, na jugu regije, direktno na moru,
5 km južno od mjesta Sibenik, 15 km jugoistočno od mjesta Vodice, 19 km sjeverno od
mjesta Primosten. Sve usluge i sadržaji u mjestu. Natkriti bazen, wellness centar, sauna,
solarij, masaža na 2 - 5 km. Daljnje mogućnosti za kupovinu i zabavu na 2 - 5 km.


EN Locatin Description Brodarica

Small, quiet, family-friendly resort with 3&#39;000 inhabitants, in the southern part of the region,
directly by the sea, 5 km south from Sibenik, 15 km south-east from Vodice, 19 km north
from Primosten. All shops, restaurants etc. in the resort. Indoor aquatic centre, wellness
centre, sauna, solarium, massage at 2 - 5 km. More possibilities for shopping and
entertainment 2 - 5 km.

DE Ortsbeschreibung Brodarica

Kleine, ruhige, familienfreundliche Ortschaft, 3&#39;000 Einwohner, im Süden der Region, direkt
am Meer, 5 km südlich von Sibenik, 15 km südöstlich von Vodice, 19 km nördlich von
Primosten. Alle Dienstleistungen im Ort. Hallenbad, Wellnesszentrum, Sauna, Solarium,
Massage in 2 - 5 km. Weitere Möglichkeiten für Einkauf und Unterhaltung in 2 - 5 km.